Class UnknownTypeException

  • java.lang.Object

          • org.jsimpledb.JSimpleDBException
            • org.jsimpledb.UnknownTypeException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class UnknownTypeException
extends JSimpleDBException
    Thrown when attempting to get the JObject associated with an ObjId that has an unrecognized type (i.e., storage ID).

    This exception should not occur during normal usage. It may occur when using both the higher-level JSimpleDB Java model object API and the lower level core database API at the same time in an incompatible way.

    See Also:
    JSimpleDB.getJObject(org.jsimpledb.core.ObjId), Serialized Form
